# ------------------------------------------------------------
# WHAT:
# - Repo-wide ignore rules for generated + sensitive files.
#
# WHY:
# - Keep secrets, dependencies, and build artifacts out of Git.
# - Prevent OS/editor noise from polluting history.
#
# HOW:
# - Ignore common output folders, caches, and env files.
# ------------------------------------------------------------

# macOS
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# Node / JS
**/node_modules/
**/npm-debug.log
**/yarn-debug.log
**/yarn-error.log

# Env files (keep .env.example)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!.env.example

# Flutter / Dart
**/.dart_tool/
**/build/
**/.flutter-plugins
**/.flutter-plugins-dependencies
**/.pub-cache/
**/.packages
**/coverage/

# IDE / Editor
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/
*.iml
*~
